OL,3,CLabour and Conservatives rule out
OL,4,Craising VAT after General Election
OL,6,FA war of words has broken out between
OL,7,FLabour and the Conservatives after
OL,8,Fboth ruled out raising VAT after the
OL,9,FGeneral Election as Political
OL,10,FCorrespondents Jasmine Cameron-
OL,11,FChileshe and Shehab Khan report
OL,13,FFinance chiefs for both the Tories and
OL,14,FLabour have ruled out raising value
OL,15,Fadded tax (VAT) if their party were to
OL,16,Fwin the on July 4.
OL,18,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt warned family
OL,19,Ffinances could be "hammered" if there
OL,20,Fwas to be a rise to taxes on products
OL,21,Fand services.
