OL,6,FIn light of his claims, Hunt urged
OL,7,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer to make
OL,8,Fa similar commitment "on camera".
OL,10,FMr Hunt also wrote: "A VAT increase
OL,11,Fwill hammer families' finances and
OL,12,Fpush inflation back up, just when we
OL,13,Fhave got it down to normal."
OL,15,FUK inflation slowed to 2.3% in April,
OL,16,Fthe lowest level since July 2021 and
OL,17,Fnear the government's 2% target,
OL,18,Faccording to the latest figures.
