OL,4,Craising VAT after General Election
OL,6,FMs Reeves said: "Labour will not be
OL,7,Fincreasing income tax, national
OL,8,Finsurance or VAT."
OL,10,F"I want taxes on working people to be
OL,11,Flower, not higher. That is why we
OL,12,Fopposed the increases to national
OL,13,Finsurance when Rishi Sunak put those
OL,14,Fforward as chancellor."
OL,16,FDuring speeches this week, Ms Reeves
OL,17,Fsaid her party has no plans to
OL,18,Fannounce new tax rises beyond already
OL,19,Fannounced policies, including a plan
OL,20,Fto charge 20% VAT on private school
OL,21,Ffees.
