OL,6,FMr Hunt has since claimed credit for
OL,7,Fthe commitment, claiming that Labour
OL,8,Fhad "buckled under pressure" to rule
OL,9,Fout VAT rises.
OL,11,FBoth parties are making their General
OL,12,FElection pledges against a challenging
OL,13,Fbackdrop. The Institute for Fiscal
OL,14,FStudies (IFS) said the next UK
OL,15,Fgovernment will face the toughest
OL,16,Ffiscal inheritance in 70 years.
OL,18,FSir Keir has refused to commit to
OL,19,Funfreezing tax thresholds, but echoed
OL,20,Fhis shadow chancellor with regards to
OL,21,Fincome tax, national insurance and VAT.
