OL,6,FAsked whether he could guarantee that
OL,7,Fa Labour government would not raise
OL,8,FVAT, and whether he would raise income
OL,9,Ftax thresholds, the Labour leader
OL,10,Fsaid: "We've been really clear about
OL,11,Fnot raising income tax and NI, and
OL,12,Fwe've said repeatedly that nothing in
OL,13,Four plans requires us to raise tax.
OL,15,F"And that's why we've been able to set
OL,16,Fout our position on VAT as well.
OL,18,F"And that's in stark contrast to a
OL,19,Fgovernment that's taken the tax burden
OL,20,Fon working people to the highest level
OL,21,Fsince the war."
